    (3219,'I WILL NOT TOLERATE MENTION OF YOUR ABNORMALITY UNDER THIS ROOF!',50),
    (3220,'Why are you worrying about YOU-KNOW-WHO, when you should be worrying about YOU-NO-POO? The constipation sensation that\'s gripping the nation!',50),
