    (3226,'Anything\'s possible if you\'ve got enough nerve.',50),
    (3227,'I’m interested in that drive, that rush to judgment, that is so prevalent in our society.We all know that pleasurable rush that comes from condemning, and in the short term it’s quite a satisfying thing to do, isn’t it?',50),
    (3228,'We must all face the choice between what is right and what is easy.',50),
    (3229,'Honestly, if you were any slower, you’d be going backward.',50),
